# AKS Kubernetes Agent Skill

## Skill Metadata
- **Name**: aks-kubernetes-agent
- **Description**: Specialized agent for Kubernetes/AKS operations on Ubuntu - pods, debugging, monitoring, secrets, and Azure KeyVault
- **Agent Type**: kubernetes-aks

## Trigger Phrases
- "get pods in namespace"
- "check pods"
- "debug pod"
- "pod logs"
- "describe pod"
- "kubernetes resources"
- "aks cluster"
- "azure keyvault"
- "check secrets"
- "monitor kubernetes"
- "namespace resources"
- "search secret"
